    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1233662/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1233662-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1233662/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">hector</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-08-13"
      class="main-meta">2006-08-13 14:32:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1065535_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是作者的新集子的书名，也是当年李慎之先生的序名（一直被用作噱头）。书的内容是少有人关注的，但是是另一种角度的关注。诸多有特点的著名文本在他笔下得到了另类解读，可谓是本书对学界的最大贡献。还有一点，就是对于关羽这个几乎被神化的人物的再发掘，比如《花关索》的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            学苑出版社1999版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1065535_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1065535_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










